Rails Devise Pundit
===================

This application was generated with the rails_apps_composer gem:
https://github.com/RailsApps/rails_apps_composer
provided by the RailsApps Project:
http://railsapps.github.io/

This application also serves as a demo for integrating Discourse's
Single-Sign-On feature as [documented here](https://meta.discourse.org/t/official-single-sign-on-for-discourse/13045/102)

